		"Details": "An internal public address page on the dropship rings out: [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[TooltipSimGameCharacterDARIUS],Darius]] \r\n\r\n\"Commander, please report to your office, your 10:00 hours briefing is ready.\" \r\nSeveral minutes later you arrive in your office to find an irate Darius, and a laughing Yang and Farah. \"Up to your elbows in the food storage again I see,\" sneers Darius.  \"Give the Commander a break Darius!\" both Yang and Sumire say almost in sync.  But your reply takes the thunder right out of Darius's angst: \"We are throwing a small party with the extra food I just found.  It is almost to its expiration date, so I would rather the crew enjoy better food than throw it out.\"",
